<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{% block title %}Your Website{% endblock %}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/styles.css') }}">

    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/custom-styles.css') }}">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>

</head>
<body>
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-white navbar-light sticky-top p-0 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
    <a href="/home" class="navbar-brand d-flex align-items-center px-4 px-lg-5">
        <h1 class="m-0 text-success">VitalMe</h1>
    </a>
    <button type="button" class="navbar-toggler me-4" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarCollapse" aria-controls="navbarCollapse" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
    </button>
    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarCollapse">
        <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto p-4 p-lg-0">
            <a href="/home" class="nav-item nav-link active">Home</a>
            <a href="/buscar-alimento" class="nav-item nav-link">Alimentos</a>
            <a href="registro-ejercicio" class="nav-item nav-link">Ejercicios</a>
            <a href="/registro-peso" class="nav-item nav-link">Progreso</a>
            <a href="/objetivos" class="nav-item nav-link">Objetivos</a>
            <a href="/comunidad" class="nav-item nav-link">Comunidad</a>
            <a href="/perfil" class="nav-item nav-link">Perfil</a>
            <a href="/logout" class="nav-item nav-link">Cerrar sesión</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>
    
    <main>
        {% for type, messages in app.session.flashbag.all() %}
            {% for message in messages %}
                <div class="alert alert-{{ type }} alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                    {{ message }}
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
            {% endfor %}
        {% endfor %}
        {% block content %}
        {% endblock %}
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="text-white py-4 mt-auto">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5 class="mb-3">Sobre Nosotros</h5>
                    <p>Somos VitalMe, una plataforma dedicada a ayudarte a llevar un estilo de vida saludable y activo. ¡Únete a nuestra comunidad hoy mismo!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <h5 class="mb-3">Enlaces Útiles</h5>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li><a href="/buscar-alimento" class="text-white">Registrar alimentos</a></li>
                        <li><a href="registro-ejercicio" class="text-white">Registrar ejercicio</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/perfil" class="text-white">Ir a mi perfil</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <h5 class="mb-3">Síguenos</h5>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-white"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i> Facebook</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-white"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i> Twitter</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-white"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i> Instagram</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- jQuery y Popper.js -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.5.4/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>


    <style>
   
        html, body {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        main {
            flex: 1 0 auto; 
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 100px;
        }
        footer {
            flex-shrink: 0;
           
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #127c04; 
            color: #ffffff; 
            border: none; 
            border-radius: 0; 
            font-weight: 500; 
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #158a05; 
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #ffffff; 
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e3e3e3; 
            box-shadow: 0 10px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 30px 40px; 
            font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .navbar-brand h1 {
            font-size: 36px; 
            font-weight: 700; 
            color: #32db1c; 
            margin-right: 40px; 
        }

        .navbar-toggler {
            border: none; 
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-item {
            margin-left: 25px; 
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-item a {
            color: #333333; 
            font-weight: 500; 
            font-size: 20px; 
        }
    </style>

